cs213.photoAlbum.simpleview

Class CmdView

  • java.lang.Object
    • cs213.photoAlbum.simpleview.CmdView

  • public class CmdView
extends java.lang.Object
    CmdView contains the main method for the Photo Album program and creates a backend, cmdview, and controller objects. CmdView handles reading in previous data from the controller for session persistence. This class accepts input from the user for creating Users for a database, and allows for login to program. If login is successfully, CmdView starts interactiveMode, which allows for various commands to add photos, albums, and more interacting with the controller object.
    Author:
    Anna Genke and Zack Colello
